Gixauidenae</AUTHOR></BIBL>, solches mit einem dridten Supplement vermehren, auch das gantze Werck, durch Subscriptionen zum zweyten mahl drucken lassen wird, wovon das Project bey Herrn Samuel Haag dem Buchbinder zu gelben Horn am Spahlenberg zu haben, auch bey ihme zu subscribiren ist.</ITEM>
parsed.explanation: The original XML separated the title and author of the same book into two distinct <BIBL> tags. To improve the semantic structure and group related bibliographic information for a single work, these two <BIBL> tags were consolidated into one, enclosing both the <TITLE> and <AUTHOR> elements. This involved removing one closing </BIBL> tag and one opening <BIBL> tag.
